{"tid":1549603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"913只係學界死線？所謂升級行動我又聽到厭。","createTime":"2019-09-07T11:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T07:54:49.000Z","uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6be18d15c064bec1e68ae0935cbd1c42e6b6643d","tid":1549603,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"首先，無記錯既話，提出913無回應就會升級既係學界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然無大台，咁913升級行動既只係學界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁依家個政府就話<strong>&quot;動議撤回&quot;</strong>勉強都叫回應該咗1項。<br />\n雖然我個人覺得都係會升級，但學界會點升級法？此其一。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其二，當係民間都會跟隨升級行動，但次次升級，我無乜大感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而某啲日子係有加強&quot;火力&quot;，最近都係831放火魔法最為轟烈。<br />\n其後，黨鐵助黑警，民間先針對多啲黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n其三，913前，99係美國國會復會，可能又有變數啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以其實係點升級？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想知點樣先可以FC晒所有疑團？<br />\n我地香港人只能贏！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c94b7909a70cf4b80bfb05146bb7361c73ce7fc0","tid":1549603,"uid":90034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5019c38d20334bcdb5df36a11dd913e2e215d29a","tid":1549603,"uid":90034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23fc0a792bc6cc33e66b87ea63cbf0577cbfb371","tid":1549603,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264845025548329e62af6702fb00f0ac37234b15","tid":1549603,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2